  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Brand Engagement Rep",
  "description": "<h2>🌟 Company Overview</h2><p><strong>Vision Organisation</strong> is a people-focused<strong> sales & marketing</strong> firm that believes in growing individuals through real-world experience.<br />Our mission is to develop confident, capable sales professionals who represent leading brands with pride, clarity, and conviction.</p><h2>🚀 Role Overview</h2><p>As part of our team, you’ll be involved in <strong>face-to-face brand engagement</strong>, working at events and outreach activities while learning practical sales and marketing skills through hands-on experience and structured training.<br />This is an <strong>on-the-ground role</strong>, ideal for those who enjoy interacting with people and learning by doing.</p><h2>🎯 What You’ll Be Doing</h2><ul><li><p>Represent client brands professionally at events, roadshows, and outreach activities</p></li><li><p>Engage customers face-to-face to communicate brand messages clearly and confidently</p></li><li><p>Build rapport and create positive brand experiences</p></li><li><p>Apply sales and communication skills learned through training to support campaign goals</p></li><li><p>Work closely with a supportive team to deliver consistent results</p></li><li><p>Participate in structured training and mentorship to grow your sales and marketing capabilities</p></li></ul><h2>🙌 What We’re Looking For</h2><ul><li><p>Comfortable interacting with people in a face-to-face environment</p></li><li><p>Motivated to learn and open to feedback</p></li><li><p>Enjoys active, on-the-ground work rather than desk-based tasks</p></li><li><p>Able to commit to a full-time role</p></li><li><p>Team-oriented with a positive and proactive attitude</p></li></ul><h2>🎓 What You’ll Gain</h2><ul><li><p>Hands-on training with real-world exposure</p></li><li><p>Mentorship and continuous learning opportunities</p></li><li><p>Skill development in communication, sales, and customer engagement</p></li><li><p>A supportive environment that encourages growth and improvement</p></li></ul><h2>📩 How to Apply</h2><p>If you’re keen to build <strong>real-world experience in sales and marketing</strong> while working with people, we’d love to hear from you.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507</p>",
